                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> A non-devil triggers or disables the slamming door hazard</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The statue takes on the visage of a handmaiden devil as a wave of unholy energy washes over the courtyard. Each creature in the courtyard must succeed at a @Check[will|dc:17|options:area-effect,inflicts:slowed] save or be @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Slowed]{Slowed 1} for as long as it remains in the courtyard. The trap then rolls initiative.</p>"
