                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The statue emits a supernaturally compelling command. Each creature in the courtyard must make a @Check[will|dc:17|options:area-effect,forced-movement] save, with results below.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature is pulled 5 feet toward the statue.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature is pulled 5 feet toward the statue and must spend the first action on its next turn making a Step toward the statue.</p>"
